# Movie Recommendation System

A content-based movie recommendation system built using Machine Learning.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- TF-IDF Vectorizer
- Cosine Similarity

## Features
- Recommends similar movies
- Uses movie metadata
- Fast recommendation generation

## How it Works
1. Combine movie features
2. Convert text to vectors using TF-IDF
3. Compute cosine similarity
4. Recommend nearest movies

## Dataset
TMDB Movie Dataset
